children.text: New version available. Please update the app:)

If you want to see pregnancy tracker data here,then you must update your last menstrual period by options menu. Now, the date you entered is wrong or out of range. The date must be bigger than 6 days and smaller than 42 weeks.
Annelerin SOHBET ALANI. Sorularınızı burada sorabilirsiniz.
Note: Every baby develops differently. This app is designed to give you a general idea of your baby's development.
